":"93b60e88518c90b922f4463d86aad3dc19f9e98f","tid":1743062,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"【黑色分化警告】對家用緊區選嚟做分化，千祈唔好中計！我要分化撚完全收皮！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743019</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"084205254324e8f9bc4d6b94d2b04e466560a401","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:43:30.000Z","msg":"國際好睇重民意走向，如果今次結果都無法壓倒性佔優ko建制，就碌柒喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742863</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45a7573d6ba17aa40a82cad6408131bfaadc018e","tid":1743062,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1800d16e281d27e9b5b4fbe34404ed7ff599d73","tid":1743062,"uid":128192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"044cc8509733fcef181332d0af09be7abc841ca8","tid":1743062,"uid":271365,"like":2,"dislike":50,"score":-48,"quote":{"pid":"1cac02ac309b9cfb6c9e301afcdf00b87b59050f","tid":1743062,"uid":267172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:53:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗屌我區選撚 含淚投票 泛民打手<br />\n你睇返我之前啲reply會見到我覺得取消區選都無所謂 但有得投就照投<br />\n<br />\n我用返之前台灣人整嘅文宣比你地班打算投廢票嘅人再考慮多次<br />\n投唔投、點樣投都係你嘅自由<br />\n但請你諗清楚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnj4HyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftnj4HyL.png&h=da7c0ff9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗比張圖藍絲啦<br />\n藍絲唔投仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"好似白票唔當廢票喎<br />\n無記錯嘅話：廢票唔當係有效票，白票計有效票<br />\n白票「棄權」都當係選民表達意願"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"咁有冇一個政黨叫（投白票）?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"投白票即係投棄權票<br />\n如果一個黨叫「投白票黨」<br />\n咁你响選票上印/剔呢個黨嘅話<br />\n咁張票係有效俾咗一個候選人嘅票<br />\n咁就唔係「白票」囉"},{"pid":"342dd7b9b0213b482c93bc598ff06e62041a41fb","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6580f113c8d5fa4bfedbdf8c9ae3d84e144d6d1","tid":1743062,"uid":59465,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"杯葛不公平選舉<br />\n要做嘅唔係唔投票<br />\n而係要令投票無法進行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"政府怕國際輿論 呢個stage佢唔會停啦<br />\n<br />\n國際好睇重民意走向，如果今次結果都無法壓倒性佔優ko建制，就碌柒喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742863</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a8faf5373f551646954d0814410ab7d3a45fe105","tid":1743062,"uid":240973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e0f92ca49ecb82c9a7b0e2a7b49412cb1393624","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6580f113c8d5fa4bfedbdf8c9ae3d84e144d6d1","tid":1743062,"uid":59465,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"杯葛不公平選舉<br />\n要做嘅唔係唔投票<br />\n而係要令投票無法進行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"我諗法係：<br />\n一係取消，可以增加國際輿論<br />\n一係有得選，但要贏盡<br />\n<br />\n宜家政府怕國際輿論，打算繼續區選，咁我地就要贏盡！！"},{"pid":"fce1335b46a251ca23535b4f0b68716447341ee6","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b34642d48ea997df30039d0488a6b80d79de5b8","tid":1743062,"uid":292644,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鄭文傑單野有冇人煲大煲上國際不停煲? 幾千張photo點黎? 係唔係林鄭俾過去?<br />\n一地兩檢既後果(呢個區選都可以用黎屌當日支持一地兩檢既人)<br />\n<br />\n區選唔好唔投,你點睇區選都好,只要係俾建制贏(只係贏就夠,唔駛大贏)<br />\n林鄭同POPO直頭可以大條道理出機關槍,所以一定要投,要正正經經咁投<br />\n<br />\n有機會,順手&quot;教&quot;下藍絲投票<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tod5ssj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftod5ssj.jpg&h=68ec4a3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:51:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"faa6dd7c578211ec840333f2ec6942ba0237f99b","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00cd58386395cca7ef89478b934b16f515eb3691","tid":1743062,"uid":312332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:14:19.000Z","msg":"11月24日區議會選舉其實係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">變相公投</span></span><br />\n<br />\n公投d咩：咪就係撐政府，定反中共囉<br />\n點計票：數真藍票，同真黃票，仲有果堆不知名獨立人士，就會知道係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三分天下，還是二元對立</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">需唔需要努力確保區議會選舉順利?</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔洗</span><br />\n<br />\n政府一直好努力想正常選舉，因為要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做比外國人睇香港係正常</span>。建制派就係一個condom，你死你事，唔關我事。<br />\n<br />\n平民都好想正常選舉，因為要拉班垃圾落台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">咁邊個最唔想選舉舉行?</span></span><br />\n咪就係condom 佢地囉<br />\n1：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">選舉失敗=建制派過去都失敗，中共會點睇呢班condom</span><br />\n2：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">建制派除左做生意果批，民建聯有幾多無家底人士痴埋去做區議員，無左個位=失去生存能力</span><br />\n3：<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以後無得claim咁多維穩費lu,辦事不力仲要claim咁多錢，short Q左啊你</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，手足們記得11月24日<br />\n記得早d去投票啊<br />\n<br />\n留意<span style=\"font-size: large;\">印仔墨水乾左先好對接</span>入箱<br />\n留意<span style=\"font-size: large;\">印仔一定要吸落圓圈範圍</span><br />\n留意<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要驗查張貼有無爛，有無印花左</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:51:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f57ea10888bc78aef16a2a8db2f9c33f3f490e3c","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:01:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d520c51b58c280b951fe389d5e49e475b13b9660","tid":1743062,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3879c05060be2f61b6aa4f1bc5fb902cf58af8b","tid":1743062,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意見到對家落選，所以會投。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec05ca710c5fa947be35b211d437e58e40a31385","tid":1743062,"uid":289622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:09:57.000Z","msg":"含L 都要投"},{"pid":"af21a44bc222c1dd48e4d5fc716ae36dd000aad3","tid":1743062,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06cf4115b207012ad10d2e8ec1bf58614aa9fd35","tid":1743062,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"【贏盡區選大行動】11月23,24 齊幫手 助區選<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨在每個投票站，設幾十個街角站，每個街站有二三十人助選，一眼睇就認出係大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n民主手足缺資源，欠缺助選員，如果大家只去投票，不去助選，輸咗議席只能後悔。<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1 22號去聯絡自己區要支持的候選人，約好23號24號助選時間及位置。<br />\n2 每個街站分配三四十人，人多再分配時間輪班。<br />\n3 有人行過，講明<span style=\"color: red;\">「今天香港亂局，完全因為保皇黨有議席，所以政府極惡横行無忌，令到百萬市民憤怒，出來反對暴政。唔想香港亂，踢走保皇黨，一定要投票(＃)號！」</span><br />\n4 【重要】保票站不衝突！有人挑釁，不回應，冷處理。離遠十步影低佢，日後放上網相討要唔要撕鳥。<br />\n<br />\n如果有多過一個似民主手足後選人，會有好大風險。<br />\n查看他 facebook/IG，五六月時有無日日發過多文，剷過政府。如果無就命令佢宣報退選，否則撕鳥。<br />\n如果兩個都有，要找佢地兩個傾掂，傾唔掂，叫佢哋曬馬(或facebook like人數)，邊位多人就出線，少人就退選。<br />\n大局最重要，一定<span style=\"color: red;\">只可一位出選</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n【贏盡區選大行動】11月23,24 齊幫手 助區選！只可一位出選<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743545</a>"},{"pid":"c56e8794a256a63eb1401f6e7df3b82bdcce6bb4","tid":1743062,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"77995a3f705a54e8969b812429dcb98bf2136fc6","tid":1743062,"uid":246158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T11:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"531ef5958e2eb1c475fc0c2a21bbe707941f6e77","tid":1743062,"uid":126837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:39:47.000Z","msg":"係呀，抗爭都唔可以犯法，要跟住敵人嘅規矩玩呀，緊係一路乖乖地含住曱近平條撚一路用返共產黨留落黎嘅制度投嫁啦，有得含唔係唔含呀嘛。香港人，反抗？口號黎嫁咋"},{"pid":"9cf932919e1cefa80377c2860c72fa367ce99a84","tid":1743062,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RyMY0O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RyMY0O.jpg&h=2caf4ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kT1VSnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkT1VSnP.jpg&h=d34ba44c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/21/222050_d035abf44b033c50832ef2eb8a4f4c83.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F21%2F222050_d035abf44b033c50832ef2eb8a4f4c83.jpeg&h=32b3c4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/21/222059_1ef89f26c813a942ed33e9ca92d762d4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F21%2F222059_1ef89f26c813a942ed33e9ca92d762d4.jpeg&h=6bffbf7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/21/222122_e688019f85f421054cd109d7c1311a20.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F21%2F222122_e688019f85f421054cd109d7c1311a20.jpeg&h=94d31ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/21/222136_f5b0b92d960b3ef814aede2a518109a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F21%2F222136_f5b0b92d960b3ef814aede2a518109a3.png&h=ca60661e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n削弱對方係重點"},{"pid":"d629f4b73b943903c4bfaf5e13a32e137df0b9db","tid":1743062,"uid"